{"tid":1120824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［收費戰狼］中外交部：遇險營救費用由個人承擔","createTime":"2019-04-23T02:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T11:26:46.000Z","uid":8478,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc504c066ce04239afffb893d06ebafc0b52b5c","tid":1120824,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"斯里蘭卡周日發生連環炸彈爆炸，導致800人死傷。丹麥首富、時裝網店ASOS最大股東波爾森（Anders Holch Povlsen）的4名子女中，有3人在慘劇中不幸喪生。以下是襲擊案最新進展：<br />\n<br />\n外交部和中國駐斯里蘭卡使館提醒中國公民近期暫勿前往斯里蘭卡，稱如中國公民在提醒發布後仍堅持前往，將給當事人帶來巨大安全風險，並使大使館難以提供有效協助。由此而產生的費用，將由個人承擔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1298c2fc3be3b75870948bfb18a0446a78e9ec67","tid":1120824,"uid":156652,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T02:55:03.000Z","msg":"遠近必收"},{"pid":"fbd6bb765d75968a5ec1b44c9473df741c848342","tid":1120824,"uid":39777,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T03:06:17.000Z","msg":"親，背後要有一個強大祖國是要收費的"},{"pid":"fb15263ed62d8b236010e9ee2ab3a2e2b0c5961b","tid":1120824,"uid":55913,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T03:19:37.000Z","msg":"你根本唔撚會救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f4a21ddf39551a40d29cbd9885758696697645","tid":1120824,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T03:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a79695f76efcc3c95522a9b69a3a69f11c6468","tid":1120824,"uid":18479,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T03:23:02.000Z","msg":"講明危險唔好去，自己堅持要去，風險自己承受唔合理咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2499d160ee7fbd84118a8a1ea3d0d600b1d879a","tid":1120824,"uid":237425,"like":1,"disli